1. *Kući* sam sinoć stigao kasno. (I arrived home late last night.)
2. Nisam vidio da si *kući* stigao. (I didn't see that you had arrived home.)
3. Odlučio sam da danas ne idem *kući*. (I decided not to go home today.)
4. Moram da *kući* odem na vrijeme. (I have to go home on time.)
5. Otišao sam *kući* da se odmorim. (I went home to rest.)
6. *Kuća* u kojoj sam odrastao bila je mala. (The house I grew up in was small.)
7. Želim da kupim novu *kuću*. (I want to buy a new house.)
8. Danas sam čistio *kuću*. (Today, I cleaned the house.)
9. *Kućni* ljubimac mi je pas. (My pet at home is a dog.)
10. Obožavam da provodim vrijeme u *kućnoj* atmosferi. (I love spending time in a homely atmosphere.)